      <ID>200</ID>
      <DefaultText>The young sona cringes, then shoves you away and beckons to Gurek. "Kill the left hand one. The old man calls."

Gurek obediently drops the Nil in his left hand into the abyss, then follows his master as the other Nil weep. 

"You see, Rem?" says the one with the mop. "He's a monster. He had poor Dal killed for *nothing*. I..." He breaks down again.

